title: "You Can't Take Criticism!" Boo-Hoo.
description: (1) There's the topic of constructive criticism, (2) then there's the topic of responding to criticism constructively, but this video is, in fact, about (3) the question of how to constructively deal with someone else handling criticism poorly.  And, sure, I guess that some of the examples are drawn from a number of known-names in "vegan drama". :-/
